OL,3,CFrom relegation to redemption: could
OL,4,CSouthampton emulate FA Cup heroes of
OL,5,C1976?
OL,7,FAfter a nightmare season in the
OL,8,FPremier League brought them only 12
OL,9,Fpoints and relegation in the 2024/25
OL,10,Fseason, Southampton could be about to
OL,11,Fhave one of their most memorable
OL,12,Fseasons ever just 12 months later.
OL,14,FNone of this looked likely when boss
OL,15,FTonda Eckert took over from Will
OL,16,FStill, who was sacked in November 2025
OL,17,Fafter two wins from the first thirteen
OL,18,Fleague games left Saints in 21st place.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
