SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776859866
OL,3,CFrom relegation to redemption: could
OL,4,CSouthampton emulate FA Cup heroes of
OL,5,C1976?
OL,7,FSaints have now gone 20 matches
OL,8,Funbeaten, meaning the worst-case
OL,9,Fscenario of back-to-back relegations
OL,10,Fhas now been replaced by a virtually
OL,11,Fguaranteed spot in the play-offs and
OL,12,Fan outside chance of promotion.
OL,14,FNormally fans and managers worry that
OL,15,Fa Cup run can be a distraction, but
OL,16,FSaints have been unstoppable on all
OL,17,Ffronts.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
