OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776859866
OL,3,CFrom relegation to redemption: could
OL,4,CSouthampton emulate FA Cup heroes of
OL,5,C1976?
OL,7,FTheir unbeaten run has included 3 FA
OL,8,FCup wins mixed in with the 17 league
OL,9,Fmatches. To achieve this, manager
OL,10,FTonda Eckert has rotated his squad
OL,11,Ffrom game to game.
OL,13,FAlmost half the team is changed from
OL,14,Fmatch to match, but the results are
OL,15,Fthe same,
OL,17,FThis consistency is down to the mantra
OL,18,Fof Eckert: finish one match and close
OL,19,Fthe chapter. As soon as one win is
OL,20,Fsecured, he starts studying the next
OL,21,Fopponent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776859866
OL,3,CFrom relegation to redemption: could
OL,4,CSouthampton emulate FA Cup heroes of
OL,5,C1976?
OL,7,FThe Southampton players love it. They
OL,8,Fsay he's meticulous in his planning,
OL,9,Fgiving them clear guidelines of what
OL,10,Fto expect from each opponent.
OL,12,FMidfielder Flynn Downes called Eckert
OL,13,Fa genius after a change in formation
OL,14,Fhelped Saints win at league leaders
OL,15,FCoventry.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
