OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776859866
OL,3,CFrom relegation to redemption: could
OL,4,CSouthampton emulate FA Cup heroes of
OL,5,C1976?
OL,7,FMeanwhile, winger Tom Fellows says
OL,8,FEckert explains how certain patterns
OL,9,Fwill emerge each game, with the former
OL,10,FWest Brom player adding that it's
OL,11,Famazing how often that pattern then
OL,12,Fappears.
OL,14,FIt means the Saints players go into
OL,15,Fevery match believing they can win.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
