OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776859866
OL,3,CFrom relegation to redemption: could
OL,4,CSouthampton emulate FA Cup heroes of
OL,5,C1976?
OL,7,FIn the FA Cup that has included
OL,8,Fvictories away at Premier League
OL,9,FFulham and at home to top-flight
OL,10,Fleaders Arsenal. So could they do the
OL,11,Fsame at Wembley against Manchester
OL,12,FCity?
OL,14,FThe timing would be a dream. Fifty
OL,15,Fyears ago second-tier Southampton
OL,16,Fupset top flight giants Manchester
OL,17,FUnited.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
