FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776859866
OL,3,CFrom relegation to redemption: could
OL,4,CSouthampton emulate FA Cup heroes of
OL,5,C1976?
OL,7,FFast forward half a century and Tonda
OL,8,FEckert's side once again play a team
OL,9,Ffrom Manchester who sit a division
OL,10,Fabove them.
OL,12,FEckert's side will be massive
OL,13,Funderdogs on Saturday April 25th, but
OL,14,Fthen it was the same on May 1st 1976.
OL,16,FPerhaps one of Southampton's strengths
OL,17,Fis the element of surprise. Most
OL,18,Fmatches see 5 or 6 changes, so the
OL,19,Fopponent can't be sure exactly who'll
OL,20,Fthey'll face.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776859866
OL,3,CFrom relegation to redemption: could
OL,4,CSouthampton emulate FA Cup heroes of
OL,5,C1976?
OL,7,FThe change in personnel has also seen
OL,8,Fnew stars emerge, including Japenese
OL,9,FMidfielder Kuryu Matski, who was
OL,10,Fbarely used in the first half of the
OL,11,Fseason.
OL,13,FHe's now an important, goal-scoring
OL,14,Faddition.
OL,16,FAt the other end of the pitch, Israel
OL,17,Fgoalkeeper Daniel Peretz was signed on
OL,18,Floan from Bayern Munich in January and
OL,19,Fhas fast become one of the top
OL,20,Fstoppers in the division.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776859866
OL,3,CFrom relegation to redemption: could
OL,4,CSouthampton emulate FA Cup heroes of
OL,5,C1976?
OL,7,FIf Saints are promoted they will no
OL,8,Fdoubt try to sign him permanently.
OL,10,FCyle Larin is also fast becoming
OL,11,Fsomething of a lucky charm, as
OL,12,FSouthampton have won nine of the ten
OL,13,Fmatches the Canadian striker has
OL,14,Fstarted since he joined on February
OL,15,F2nd.
OL,17,FManchester City have global megastars
OL,18,Fall over the pitch, like striker
OL,19,FErling Haaland and goalkeeper
OL,20,FGianluigi Donnarumma.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
