PN,41210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776859866
OL,3,CFrom relegation to redemption: could
OL,4,CSouthampton emulate FA Cup heroes of
OL,5,C1976?
OL,7,FThey are overwhelming favourites, but
OL,8,Fany complacency on their part could
OL,9,Fwell be exploited, particularly with a
OL,10,Ftight title race involving Arsenal at
OL,11,Fthe forefront of their minds.
OL,13,FHalf a century on from Southampton's
OL,14,Fhistoric FA Cup win, the club is very
OL,15,Fkeen to mark the 50th anniversary in
OL,16,Fstyle.
OL,18,FThey produced yellow commemorative
OL,19,Fshirts before their FA Cup campaign
OL,20,Fbegan, to remember the kit worn in
OL,21,F1976.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
