PN,41211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776859866
OL,3,CFrom relegation to redemption: could
OL,4,CSouthampton emulate FA Cup heroes of
OL,5,C1976?
OL,7,FThe plan was for the team to wear the
OL,8,Fnew kit for every FA Cup match this
OL,9,Fseason, and avoiding yellow-shirted
OL,10,Frivals Norwich or Watford has ensured
OL,11,Fthe players have been able to wear the
OL,12,FYellow shirts throughout the campaign.
OL,14,FThe FA has now approved the same again
OL,15,Fat Wembley, so the 33,000 Southampton
OL,16,Ffans heading to the game have vowed to
OL,17,Fwear the colour too and make Wembley
OL,18,FWay a sea of yellow
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
